{"tid":241793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疑拍三級片被馬會踢走　《同班同學》麥芷誼：shame on you","createTime":"2017-05-13T12:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T21:55:57.000Z","uid":15991,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a84e504935cc88a23bfb5aed404a323da2f3630","tid":241793,"uid":15991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱話/90458/疑拍彭浩翔三級片被馬會踢走-同班同學-麥芷誼-shame-on-you#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F90458%2F%E7%96%91%E6%8B%8D%E5%BD%AD%E6%B5%A9%E7%BF%94%E4%B8%89%E7%B4%9A%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%B8%A2%E8%B5%B0-%E5%90%8C%E7%8F%AD%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8-%E9%BA%A5%E8%8A%B7%E8%AA%BC-shame-on-you%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D17&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=92f5f20f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱話/90458/疑拍彭浩翔三級片被馬會踢走-同班同學-麥芷誼-shame-on-you#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=17</a><br />\n<br />\n曾全裸演出《同班同學》，及客串最近大熱《春嬌救志明》的Koyi麥芷誼，日前於facebook發文稱：「係香港呢片道德高地，拍過三級片或者真係會同殺過人放過火同Level。」，又指「就算你interview過關，上Training表現好，一被發現拍過三級片，Opps, sorry you are out. HKJC, shame on you.」她在留言中，暗指馬會疑因她曾參演三級片，無理解除她在馬會工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/573878/xlarge/38d76547b245a7f3f28b65eeed18fa31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F573878%2Fxlarge%2F38d76547b245a7f3f28b65eeed18fa31.jpg&h=b9875356&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a210adc513fcc1de61d5716188f660b642497a8","tid":241793,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20df08c981c4ce21e6a98cbfc3f438113b8cc00","tid":241793,"uid":15991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T12:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20151104/photo/bkn-20151104224307896-1104_00862_001_02b.jpg?2015